SUMMARY:Game Night
DESCRIPTION:Meet People Lancaster\nFriday\, April 10th is board game night
  at Neighbors Cafe & afterparty at Decades Lancaster!\n\nNeighbors Cafe ha
 s several board games there but please bring your favorite game along to s
 hare!\n\nGame Night @📍Neighbors Cafe: 6:30PM-8PM\n\nAfterparty @📍Dec
 ades : 8:15PM-10:00PM (but you can stay later if the party is still going 
 strong)\n\nCost: Free to attend\, but please support Neighbors with a drin
 k purchase as a thanks for hosting us and please tip your barista. Please 
 tip your bartender @ Decades and make sure you settle your tab there befor
 e leaving for the night.\n\nmeet people Lancaster • Lancaster things to 
 do • Lancaster events • neighbors cafe • decades Lancaster
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meet-people-lancaster/events/31416582
