SUMMARY:Decades Night
DESCRIPTION:Meet People Lancaster\n⚡️ DECADES NIGHT WITH CENTRAL PA SO
 LOs GROUP ⚡️\n\nMeet at 7pm at Decades on Friday\, April 17th\, 2026 f
 or a do as you please gaming & bowling evening! We will hopefully try and 
 get a table upstairs in the loft for people who’d like to eat or bring t
 heir own board games — we will also try and get a bowling lane group tog
 ether!\n\n📍 Decades Lancaster - 438 N. Queen Street\, Lanc 17603\n\nPle
 ase support local by purchasing drinks & food and remember to close your t
 ab & tip your bartenders before you leave for the evening!\n\nHost: Chris 
 Rohrbaugh - Central PA SOLOs Group\n.\nmeet people Lancaster • central P
 a solos • meet up • decades Lancaster • Lancaster meet up group • 
 games night • stuff to do Lancaster Pa
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/meet-people-lancaster/events/31416588
